description: Trophy Resources, Inc. operates as an independent natural resource company in North America. Its oil interests are in the Fort Worth Basin in central Texas and the Casper Arch/Wind River Basin in Wyoming. Trophy Resources has a joint venture partnership with Russell Industries, Inc. and American Uranium Mining Company for developing the companies' commercial holdings in uranium, oil, and natural gas. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Alpharetta, Georgia.
